data.value:
Changelog: - REWROTE FROM SCRATCH! - Improved GUI, modern style. - Improved loading times for startup, list loading, etc. - Improved search function - Added list creation by database - Added function to add staged pets (unfortunately with 0 durability) - Added bufffunction for pets - Added buttons for Soul Catalyst and other items - Added set creature value command - Added kill target command - Fixed huntaholic command
This is the final version (except for bugfixes or new commands)!
